{"type": "article", "id": 22987, "title": "“冰淇淋三明治”包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-29T07:08:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 51, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021052350w2d98Ku3aShE1Cs.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一组“冰淇淋三明治”（ice cream sandwiches）的甜品包装设计，选用了清新而略带复古的风格。立方体的盒子以黑白两色为主，间隔有彩色的点缀来表现不同的口味。纸质的包装使用了黑白网格，就像野餐时需要打开的布，上面贴有荷叶边的标签让这它多了一份童真和可爱。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105232fgMLpXltuSP7VH0N.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105233TdZxP4OJmj8aL7oD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105233e0ZwkJWAM9la4sVc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105234GM59kuw0IlpC2RVf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105234w2UCBj4YtJAsNvEX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}